  "text": "The short random primer (OPU 15) and reference dermatophyte isolates were used to identify some isolated dermatophytes. The PCR amplified productions are summarized in Table 3 . Six species (T. violaceum. T. rubrum, T. verrucosum, T. mentagrophytes, M. canis and E. floccosum) were identified by this primer. To identify the remaining isolates, the PCR amplified productions of OPD 18 were compared with the study of Liu and his colleagues [CITATION_1] (Table 4) . To calculate the similarity, the following equation was used [CITATION_2] .",
